Package: glossary.ipbes.ipcc
Title: Compare IPBES and IPCC Glossaries
Version: 0.5.0
Author: IPBES TSU Knowledge and Data [aut, cre] (ORCID:
    <https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4511-3407>), Claude Code [ctb], Codex [ctb]
