Description: A Shiny application that loads the IPBES biodiversity glossary
    and the IPCC climate change glossary, merges them by term, and displays
    definitions side-by-side with text similarity scores and word-level diffs.
    The IPCC glossary can be refreshed from the live IPCC website within the app,
    with hosted-safe mode available for shinyapps.io deployments.
